    <title>Markdown Basics for Github Style</title>
    <url>/en/archives/f283b71.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\en\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\en\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\en\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h1 id="11"> 前言 </h1>
制作Hexo个人网站时，通常都会使用Markdown作为写文章的工具。虽然之前自学过，但是还是希望重新巩固一下。

<p>本文将包含了Markdown所有的知识点，并配以案例和演示，以及使用过程中的一些tips。文中介绍的Markdown是针对于Github风格的，其他风格也会有所提及。我使用的是Atom来编辑md文件，在Atom中预览markdown文件，只需要<br>点击Packages -&gt; Markdown Preview -&gt; Toggle Github Style</p>
<p>希望有所帮助，方便随时查询。</p>
<span id="more"></span>



<h1 id="22"> <font color=red>标题</font></h1>

<p>标题有两种形式：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>第一种,</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">一级标题,下面加“===”</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">===</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">二级标题,下面加“---”</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>第二种，</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题  </span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题  </span><br><span class="line">### 三级标题  </span><br><span class="line">#### 四级标题  </span><br><span class="line">##### 五级标题  </span><br><span class="line">###### 六级标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>第一种，<br><img src="/images/Markdown-Basics-for-Github-Style/Title_1.png" alt="第一种"></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>第二种，<br><img src="/images/Markdown-Basics-for-Github-Style/Title_2.png" alt="第二种"></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Github风格一二三级标题会有下划线，其他风格是一二级</li>
<li>标题和下一行有间距</li>
<li>Github风格的标题是 === or —, 其他只需要 = or -</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h1 id="33"> <font color=red>字体</font> </h1>

<p>下面是常用Markdown字体操作，</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">**双星是粗体**  </span><br><span class="line">__双下滑线是粗体__</span><br><span class="line">*单星是斜体*</span><br><span class="line">_单下滑线是斜体_</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是黑体字<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;微软雅黑&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是微软雅黑<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;STCAIYUN&quot;</span>&gt;</span>我是华文彩云<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">red</span>&gt;</span>我是红色<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">#008000</span>&gt;</span>我是绿色<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">Blue</span>&gt;</span>我是蓝色<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">5</span>&gt;</span>我是尺寸<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;黑体&quot;</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">green</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">5</span>&gt;</span>我是黑体，绿色，尺寸为5<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">font</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">bgcolor</span>=<span class="string">yellow</span>&gt;</span>背景色yellow<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong></p>
<blockquote>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>两星是粗体</strong><br><strong>两下滑线是粗体</strong><br><em>单星是斜体</em><br><em>单是斜体</em><br><font face="黑体">我是黑体字</font><br><font face="微软雅黑">我是微软雅黑</font><br><font face="STCAIYUN">我是华文彩云</font><br><font color=red>我是红色</font><br><font color=#008000>我是绿色</font><br><font color=Blue>我是蓝色</font><br><font size=5>我是尺寸</font><br><font face="黑体" color=green size=5>我是黑体，绿色，尺寸为5</font></p>
<table><tr><td bgcolor=yellow>背景色yellow</td></tr></table>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h1 id="44">  <font color=red>分隔线</font></h1>
分割线上面要空一行才能生效
<figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet"></span><span class="section">* * *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">- - -</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">----------</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
>**效果如下:**
***


<hr>
<h1 id="删除线-下划线"><a href="#删除线-下划线" class="headerlink" title="删除线 | 下划线"></a><font color=red>删除线 | 下划线</font></h1><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~DELETE~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span>UNDERLINE<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong><br><del>DELETE</del><br><u>UNDERLINE</u></p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h1 id="脚注"><a href="#脚注" class="headerlink" title="脚注"></a><font color=red>脚注</font></h1><p>正常Markdown的脚注：</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">跳转至脚注内容 [^RUNOOB]。</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">^RUNOOB</span>]: <span class="link">脚注内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Github模式支持的脚注：</p>
<figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">I want <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span> [FT](#myfootnote1) <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;myfootnote1&quot;</span>&gt;</span>FT<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span>: Footnote content</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong><br>I want <sup><a href="#myfootnote1">FT</a></sup><br><a name="myfootnote1">FT</a>: Footnote content is Here</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h1 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a><font color=red>列表</font></h1><p>Markdown列表分为 <strong>无序列表</strong>，<strong>有序列表</strong> 和 <strong>嵌套列表</strong> 。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>无序列表</strong>，</p>
</blockquote>
<pre><code>* One
* Two
* Three

+ One
+ Two
+ Three

- One
- Two
- Three
</code></pre>
<blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>One</li>
<li>Two</li>
<li>Three</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>有序列表</strong>，</p>
</blockquote>
<pre><code>1. One
2. Two
3. Three
</code></pre>
<blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<ol>
<li>One</li>
<li>Two</li>
<li>Three</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>嵌套列表</strong>，</p>
</blockquote>
<p>+-*可以任意组合， 前面的空格代表嵌套层数，后面的空格不能少</p>
<pre><code>- 嵌套列表，0个空格
 + 嵌套列表，1个空格
  + 嵌套列表，2个空格(无变化)
   - 嵌套列表，3个空格
* 嵌套列表5
  - 嵌套列表6
</code></pre>
<blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong></p>
</blockquote>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>嵌套列表，0个空格</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>嵌套列表，1个空格</li>
<li>嵌套列表，2个空格(无变化）</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>嵌套列表，3个空格</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>嵌套列表5<ul>
<li>嵌套列表6</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="区块"><a href="#区块" class="headerlink" title="区块"></a><font color=red>区块</font></h1><blockquote>
<ol>
<li><strong>段落用 &gt; 的个数表示段落层次，</strong></li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<pre><code>&gt; 区块1
&gt;&gt; 区块1.1
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; 区块1.1.N
-----------【这里有空行】------------
&gt; 区块2
&gt;&gt; 区块2.1
&gt;&gt;&gt; 区块2.1.1
</code></pre>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>效果如下:</strong></p>
</blockquote>
